<h2>Use Extreme Caution with Macaroni Code You Didn't Write</h2>
<p>
Macaroni makes extensive use Lua scripts. Because it mixes them in with typical 
source code, this means that
<b>any program code you download can harm your machine even if all you're doing
is running something innocent like "clean".</b> This is typically the case 
with Makefiles and the like
but Macaroni makes harming other peoples machines even easier.
</p>


